Download New Jersey car accident records for a given year

Source: R/download_data.R
get_njtr1.Rd

Download New Jersey car accident records for a given year

get_njtr1(year, type, geo = FALSE)

Arguments

year

Year to download crash data for
type

The table of NJDOT crash data to download
geo

Logical, whether to filter only to geotagged cases (default = FALSE)

Value

tibble of all reported accidents for the year

Examples

get_njtr1(year = 2019, type = "Pedestrians")
